Diamond::

She walked to the entrance of the base."KitKat, I have brought them 
here and getting them situated for you. You can talk to them when 
your ready."

Diamond looked back at the other bots. She shook her head. She was 
leting her emotion chip get in the way. She turned and looked down 
the hall.  She refocused on her mission.  She got a evil grin on her 
face. She would enjoy this mission, just as she enjoyed her other 
missions. She just enjoyed killing.
